{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>李家鼎（鼎爺）前妻施明的喪禮於今日（4月22日）於大圍寶福紀念館設靈，李家鼎與細孖李泳豪在儀式完畢後離開靈堂，鼎爺由李泳豪攙扶下步出靈堂，神情哀傷，步履蹣跚。原來李家鼎離開靈堂後，在靈堂外的街道食杯麵，畫面令人唏噓，食完杯麵後，兩人又再折返靈堂。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123686409224589312083245.jpeg/ipTZyKD6SZik2J_I8P5tkxoA-h_vz-3jvugymIjoMpg\" alt=\"李家鼎離開靈堂企街食杯麵。（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>李家鼎離開靈堂企街食杯麵。（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123686406372331520560921.jpeg/9DRbI3Yjknug-P50y7527TqRi0MIrUGhMo2bXQSNm10\" alt=\"李家鼎離開靈堂企街食杯麵。（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>李家鼎離開靈堂企街食杯麵。（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123693327800209408864205.jpeg/itGrsn-yPAYJWrWMhPhjoyEeFakL2ITdrGYm_ppmJv4\" alt=\"（陳順禎攝）\"><figcaption>（陳順禎攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123693325098946560182647.jpeg/gh54cSkEeUO_Lsl0qTITVIi4YOJB1q8qVkPqwmBD6sI\" alt=\"（陳順禎攝）\"><figcaption>（陳順禎攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123686772669157376283691.jpeg/YLkW70Mzxx5V-nW6txdlNE-pFpr47ndrsukPF4TpDxc\" alt=\"兩人又再折返靈堂。（陳順禎攝）\"><figcaption>兩人又再折返靈堂。（陳順禎攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123686403620737024398651.jpeg/baOqQNc6NAhGVI2ooVH7aJJvCXqb2PX3y2Fyaf1hcmk\" alt=\"兩人又再折返靈堂。（陳順禎攝）\"><figcaption>兩人又再折返靈堂。（陳順禎攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-22T11:00:36.973480+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":209,"images":6,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}